text: Boa is one of 14 Barangays of the municipality of Cagdianao, Dinagat Islands, Philippines, it is situated in the southeast portion of the province.Boa, Dinagat Islands - Google Maps ==Education== The barangay hosts the Boa Elementary School which was established, January 01, 1965 and is part of the Albor District.Boa Elementary School == References == == External links == * Province of Dinagat Islands - Official webpage * Boa Elementary School Category:Philippines geography stubs Category:Barangays of Dinagat Islands
